These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-1::.
7 different games are played: poker, chess, backgammon, whist, snooker, go, bridge
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing go is on the far right##1
7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
8. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |     5      |    6    |    7     |
| Game   | bridge | whist | poker | chess | backgammon | snooker | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, british, indian, egyptian, indonesian, spanish
 1. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
 2. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the spanish##5
 3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 4. the egyptian is on the left of the argentine##1
 5. the argentine is on the left of the british##1
 6. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the spanish##5
 7. the indian is on the left of the indonesian##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 9. the indonesian is between the egyptian and the indian##2
10. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
11. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |  2  |    3     |    4    |     5      |  6   |  7  |
| Nationality   | spanish | nigerian | indian | indonesian | egyptian | argentine | british |

