.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-3::.
There 7 different types of food: pear, corn, cauliflower, mango, apricot, banana, blueberry
1. the person eating apricot is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating pear##2
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating corn and the person eating blueberry##2
5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating pear##1
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
7. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Food   | corn | cauliflower | blueberry | apricot | pear | banana | mango |

