.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bolivar, alhambra, game, chaman, aristoff, tiparillo
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
3. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
4. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the chaman-smoker##5
5. the alhambra-smoker is between the game-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
6. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
7. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
8. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
9. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3     |    4    |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | game | alhambra | siglo | bolivar | chaman | aristoff |

