.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: romance, fantasy, spy, martial-arts, epic, thriller, action
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
2. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
9. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | epic | martial-arts | romance | fantasy | action | thriller |

