2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
4. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
5. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
7. the person playing billiard is between the person playing go and the person playing scrabble##2
8. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5     |    6     |     7     |
| Game   | domino | go | billiard | scrabble | bridge | whist | mah-jongg |

