.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-14::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, may, july, february, october, november, march
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |    2     |  3  |  4   |   5    |   6    |   7   |
| Birthday   | february | july | november | may | march | june | october |

