.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-5-15::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, balloon-flower, sunflower, bellflower, begonia, aconite
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 2. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
 5. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
 6. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
10. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |   3   |   4    |  5   |  6   |  7   |
| Flower   | aconite | balloon-flower | bellflower | sunflower | poppy | begonia | rose |

